# SSH-Tool

This cli tool allows you to create and manage your SSH config file.

## Installation

```bash
pip install ssh-cli
```

## Usage

```bash
ssh-cli
```

## Features

- Add a new host (with or without a key)
- Remove a host
- List all hosts
- Connect to a host
- Edit ssh config file
- Cleanup SSH keys
